This document desribe how to upgrade from HPT 1.2 to HPT 1.4.

1. AreaFixKillReports token is deprecated now. Change it to:
    AreafixReportsAttr loc pvt k/s npd         # kill areafix reports
      or
    AreafixReportsAttr loc pvt k/s npd dir     # kill areafix reports and
                                               # send it's directly
